{"type": "article", "id": 21896, "title": "多功能扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-04T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145831g8wz0LHPca2qSIis.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">法国高端音响生产商 LA BOITE 在家博会上发布了一款多功能扬声器，有点类似老式的录音机，他们希望能播放任何形式的音源。打开盖子后是一款留声机，也可以放 CD，通过蓝牙连接上智能设备。音质上，由电音博士 yvon maurel 和 R&amp;D 实验室一起实验，偏细腻。扬声器是用橡木和铝合金材质制作，高度正好是一个小桌子，可以当做书桌台。<a href=\"http://laboiteconcept.com/en/lp-160-home.php\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214582659DPERoWM2e8v7yn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145827s5nmbUDzARSjrpZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145828Ct2PJfsZGaNk1Wj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145829VgWvacsB1lEMHoPx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145831pUaMj5SQGFc2nvNk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}